    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. This example remains mechanically peerless, with proactive rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power through a variable M differential lock for superlative corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its factory-spec kinematic precision, benefiting from a complete bushing refresh and perfectly damped struts. Presented in concours-level condition with an immaculate underbody and zero mechanical fatigue, this is a turn-key acquisition for the discerning purist.",
