      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish retains its original deep luster, protected by a professional ceramic coating, with zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains indistinguishable from new; the premium leather is supple and free of any creasing, and the factory-fresh scent is still present. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It has never seen rain or snow and has been driven sparingly only on clear weekend afternoons. Included are both original keys, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership floor.",
